---
description: "API Controller rules"
alwaysApply: true
---

# Controller Rules

- Controllers must be thin
- No business logic inside controller

# Input/Output
- Use DTOs only
- Never expose EF entities

# Response
- Use consistent response format
- Use ProblemDetails for errors

# Async
- All endpoints must be async

# Status Codes
- 200 OK → success
- 201 Created → create
- 400 → validation error
- 404 → not found